:34:29.000Z","msg":"不要說推，請說<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內，近距離開槍射擊<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n6. 警犬在太古站推人落電梯<br />\n7. 荃灣攻擊平民"},{"pid":"68fbfae6fe2ea3ebcbd03fec598558dca9d4612d","tid":1457810,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe0c55cbfdae86b0c046e07b778668497f4fd19","tid":1457810,"uid":251366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f53b5e029064df89a17af0d781214c2b44daaa8","tid":1457810,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:21:53.000Z","msg":"商界最怕一樣嘢，就係估你唔到（uncertainty）。任何一樣嘢長期發生就必定估到（certainty)，商界就會有對策。因此，連續N日令機場癱瘓、連續佔領道路等行動對商界個影響冇突發性癱瘓機場咁金。如果N日冇機場，商界可以安排車隊，如果N日塞路，商界可以改路。但如果有機場但又唔知幾時要關閉，咁就效應大。效應要大必要估你唔到。<br />\n<br />\nWater嘅形態正正係估佢唔到。<br />\n<br />\nBe water。<br />\n<br />\n經濟手段好撚有用，一定要繼續！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457461</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:37:26.000Z","msg":"成功在就係決定落得快 對手冇時間準備 琴日仲有人話時間太急等埋文宣真係笑左  打仗切忌優柔寡斷 兵多都冇用 睇下袁紹係點輸俾曹操就知"},{"pid":"b81893189f9f07a99bd3de1644bf4eb4fea1f1b1","tid":1457810,"uid":252151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:37:58.000Z","msg":"721!<br />\n811!"},{"pid":"204b01788b4ee5d7043b9e3b0eca460d1bdaf5f0","tid":1457810,"uid":72745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:49:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9cbad3728f09f9a6b16e8ac7df6bbb1c8f1fca6f","tid":1457810,"uid":106663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:50:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">BE WATER<br />\nBE HUMBLE</span></span>"},{"pid":"16afdf28ad24ad362505a80ec9cc52091ac414e2","tid":1457810,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:51:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c2a67ba9cb3e4509217465bf8b1d98c85c9215a","tid":1457810,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:57:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa8709e2a6ffd637a81d11e120d84e3faeebdd98","tid":1457810,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:57:56.000Z","msg":"由得警方御用暴徒自己衝防線<br />\n入得機場請保持克制<br />\n和理非可以睇表演如何鎮壓、如何自編自導<br />\n<br />\n下次唔洗再問去定留 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f310UGJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff310UGJ.jpg&h=61673d36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dba29e2b7ab0700a6c4a4f2017e2a8d9465ee8cb","tid":1457810,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:04:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4b38dcfdb81c8d87487a55de5dab44ada940f021","tid":1457810,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655960f33d7d376d2a697a525beb604d773136f2","tid":1457810,"uid":185854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"團結先係最大武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523bde44620cfb2ac86e94435c9f91696ee3dc67","tid":1457810,"uid":67424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"593c2ed44278fa786b763528174fc123e009f20b","tid":1457810,"uid":282798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:10:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"de16f2134a5a7474ab7dad304ae9d558fa9039ce","tid":1457810,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:22:12.000Z","msg":"走同留都好,唔好互屌,唔係又變14年咁"},{"pid":"ff472009151833a7d2360fffa2ce1b6b8a546010","tid":1457810,"uid":292235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:25:57.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"a5ac6c736b9c045defe51f58acb8402dbb684a4b","tid":1457810,"uid":151730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:34:27.000Z","msg":"實用文，推，勿忘721，811"},{"pid":"b1e6662a3c3cad7010df4d125a654b6a0a730104","tid":1457810,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9e5c9b48daef6c5828dfd3ba41b8d8816aff2de","tid":1457810,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab366e56ac161ddbc3e1d6e17e56d8182544fe67","tid":1457810,"uid":5995,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:23:19.000Z","msg":"你邊位呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:28:57.000Z","msg":"又係對事不對人<br />\n<br />\n理想國度係不因人廢言，法律及道理面前人人平等"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:45:13.000Z","msg":"咪理條傻膠"},{"pid":"9bbabb4bebbf8acf12a63ad8f14bc0f989adeff6","tid":1457810,"uid":80592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:00:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">冷靜思考做嗰決定係咪幫到件事<br />\n<br />\n文宣戰好撚重要<br />\n所有<span style=\"color: red;\">行動</span>都需要<span style=\"color: red;\">宣傳</span><br />\n要<span style=\"color: red;\">反制國家宣傳機器</span><br />\n唔好咁容易信<span style=\"color: red;\">假消息</span><br />\n要話俾世界知我哋咁做嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">原因</span><br />\n喺文宣 網絡世界都要 <span style=\"color: red;\">Be humble</span><br />\n做事手法好重要<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">811</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">721</span>嘅事一定要俾全世界知<br />\n<br />\n記者日日問721 811<br />\n831 五大訴求真普選百萬大遊行<br />\n要撐到9月搞大罷課<br />\n</div></strong></span><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">雖然抗爭時間久了，但絕對不能忘記，\n我們一直以來的理念，一定要堅持下去。</code></pre><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">繼續大力做藍絲文宣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做事手法好重要<br />\n要反制國家宣傳機器 文宣要大大力做<br />\n對內：AirDrop同路人 行動 戰略 方向 打氣<br />\n對外：Facebook 假acc<span style=\"color: red;\">扮中立</span>拉攏藍絲<br />\nWhatsApp放<span style=\"color: red;\">分化</span>藍絲嘅圖<br />\n用返<span style=\"color: red;\">煽情</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">假消息</span>老點佢哋<br />\n地鐵站貼文宣 播片<br />\n國際：機場派外文文宣 播英文片<br />\n最新可以派埋文宣USB<br />\nQR Code 無用 無人會scan<br />\n</div></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DrLgUUu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrLgUUu.png&h=6550a2e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28K11o3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28K11o3.png&h=985d7652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">冷靜思考 謀求對策</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">對準政權 勿生雜念</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n</div></strong>"},{"pid":"7dbde5de0bf737773797c160f88f7ec2ca6e14db","tid":1457810,"uid":207942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:00:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48b9df0d540491465c14e5e396f49197d0cdfd85","tid":1457810,"uid":8745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"c0d97174c70274ec3dfc787269aa6d1347b712ac","tid":1457810,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續推先"},{"pid":"c2bb2ed4b277ee3712d8d07addb1a23c6479942b","tid":1457810,"uid":200245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:43:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b46eee5c218c9a7327852b0c83b1f0b8d9567b0b","tid":1457810,"uid":172345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08